Subject: [VB] Different FIRE hazard


I'm posting this to both lists, since it's a universal problem. I've
been helping a friend get a 77 bus back on the road. As with many
air-cooleds, it has some profuse oil leaks in it. Well, after a brief
shakedown drive around the block, I pulled back into my driveway, got
out, and noticed more smoke than usual coming from under the passenger
side of the engine. A quick look revealed orange flames on top of the
heater box, and growing larger.

